node.text: I really enjoyed my conversation with @thecindygram, Editor-in-Chief of @interiordesignmag, on DesignBiz! Cindy and I discuss connecting to nature, a seamless transition between indoors and outdoors, and sustainability.

node.text: Renderings have become such an integral part of what we do. This one is for the ultimate fitness buff. A concept for a client a while back fit for any Olympic athlete that pushes the limits of what a gym can be that includes an indoor outdoor swimming pool, tilting walls a glass to take the work out outside,  a boxing ring as well as a climbing wall and all manner of weight racks and exercise machines. The only limit his imagination and how determined you are. Hope everyone has a much more restful Sunday, looking at this image is probably enough of a work out for the day😉 #fitness #goals #ultimate #gym #boxing #climbing #weights #running #swimming #indoor #outdoor #olympics
